comments: [Observable in enhanced video] RAR shows Curry (GSW) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Capela (HOU) legally contests Curry's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) has his arm extended when he releases from the contact with Durant (GSW) but he does not dislodge him from his position.
Durant (GSW) makes marginal contact with Harden (HOU) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Durant's (GSW) arm but does not affect his ability to defend the shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Paul's (HOU) pass.
Tucker (HOU) and Thompson (GSW) make incidental contact with one another as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Tucker (HOU) makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) that does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Iguodala (GSW) is already in Tucker's (HOU) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gordon (HOU) is already in Iguodala's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Curry (GSW) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) arm that affects his drive to the basket.
Green (GSW) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Durant (GSW) as Durant is starting his upward shooting motion.
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact with Tucker (HOU) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Rivers (HOU) is already in Thompson's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Green (GSW) does not fully clear the lane is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal contact with Paul (HOU) that does not affect his ability to gather the ball.  Thompson then cleanly gets his hand on the ball and a jump ball is correctly whistled.
Paul (HOU) jumps into Thompson (GSW) and makes contact to Thompson's arm that affects his ability to get to the jump ball.
Harden (HOU) engages with Iguodala (GSW) but does not affect his ability to get to the ball.
Iguodala (GSW) is already in Rivers' (HOU) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
LLS shows Paul (HOU) avoids making contact with Curry (GSW) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
RAR shows Iguodala (GSW) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Harden's (HOU) drive to the basket.
RAR shows Harden (HOU) veers into Iguodala (GSW), who maintains legal guarding position as he defends the shot attempt.  The contact by Harden does not dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
Durant (GSW) legally contests Harden's (HOU) shot near the rim.
Durant (GSW) is in bounds when the ball makes contact with him.
Iguodala (GSW) and Paul (HOU) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Rivers (HOU) is already in Iguodala's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Rivers (HOU) is already in Iguodala's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Iguodala (GSW) does not clamp Rivers' (HOU) arm as they disengage.
Harden (HOU) gathers the ball on his left foot and makes a legal move prior to the jump shot.
Green (GSW) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path and he briefly grasps Gordon's jersey as they disengage.
Rivers (HOU) makes contact to Durant's (GSW) elbow that affects his jump shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) drives through the space of Green (GSW), who is established in a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area.
Iguodala (GSW) does not make contact with Harden's (HOU) arm as he defends the shot attempt.
The shot is imminent when Durant (GSW) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for three seconds.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Rivers' (HOU) path and he does not deliver contact.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal contact with Paul (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
